title: Love The Place You Live At Woodbridge Apartments
posting_body: ['The Woodbridge Apartments', 'show contact info', 'OFFICE HOURS MON-FRI 9:00AM - 5:30PM SATURDAYS 10-5PM', 'To reserve your future unit a deposit, admin, and application fee are required.', 'Deposit: 1br $100.00 2br $200.00', 'Application: $50.00 per Adult 18 or older.', 'Admin: $150.00', 'The Woodbridge Apartments in Dallas, Texas, is the perfect community for anyone looking for a secluded community with the convenience to the city.', 'The Woodbridge is a short distance from shopping at North Park and The Galleria Mall as well as Uptown and Downtown Dallas.', 'Relax at home in our resort sized swimming pools or entertain in our spacious courtyard area.', 'Live in style while not breaking the bank!', 'If you are looking for clean, quiet and well maintained with a side of adventure, The Woodbridge is your new home!', 'Community Amenities:', 'Ceiling Fans', '2 Sparkling Swimming Pools', 'New Fitness Center', 'Clothes Care Centers', 'Pet Friendly', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', "Fath's 30-Day Satisfaction Guarantee", 'On-Site Maintenance', 'Gated Community', 'On-Site Management']
